data.description: Country living only 5 minutes from Interstate 16 and 10 minutes from Vidalia! This home features an open living floor plan. The den is HUGE and has a buck stove that will keep you cozy this winter! The den opens to the dining area and kitchen. Down the hall you will find two spacious guest rooms and a hall bath. The master suite has a private bath. Out in the great outdoors, you will enjoy a front porch perfect for a swing or rockers. In the back, plenty of land to explore, including a possible future pond site. The pole barn provides a place for equipment storage or just tinkering around. Partial fencing creates a perfect space for a few horses and there's plenty of room to add a stable. Beautiful hardwoods around the property lend their limbs for a tire swing, and life just couldn't be better than that! Fiber internet is also available. Call today for a private showing!
